quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,234,aur jo log tum mein se mrjayin aur aurtain chore jayen to aurtain chaar mahinay das din apne aap ko rokay rahen. aur jab ( yeh ) adt poori krchkin aur apne haq mein pasandeeda kaam ( yani nikah ) karlen to un par kuch gunah nahi. aur khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  2,235,aur agar tum knaye ki baton mein aurton ko nikah ka pegham bhaijho ya ( nikah ki khwahish ko ) apne dilon mein makhfi rakho to to tum par kuch gunah nahi. khuda ko maloom hai ke tum un se ( nikah ka ) zikar karo ge. magar ( ayyaam adt mein ) is ke siwa ke dastoor ke mutabiq koi baat keh do posheeda tor par un se qoul wa iqraar nah karna. aur jab taq adt poori nah haulay nikah ka pukhta iradah nah karna. aur jaan rakho ke jo kuch tumahray dilon mein hai khuda ko sab maloom hai to is se drtay raho aur jaan rakho ke khuda bakhsnay wala aur halm wala hai
  2,236,aur agar tum aurton ko un ke paas jaane ya un ka mohar muqarrar karne se pehlay Talaq day do to tum par kuch gunah nahi. haan un ko dastoor ke mutabiq kuch kharch zaroor do ( yani ) Maqdoor wala apne Maqdoor ke mutabiq day aur tangdast apni hesiyat ke mutabiq. naik logon par yeh aik terhan ka haq hai
  2,237,aur agar tum aurton ko un ke paas jaane se pehlay Talaq day do lekin mohar muqarrar kar chukay ho to aadha mohar dena hoga. haan agar aurtain mohar bakhash den ya mard jin ke haath mein Aqab nikah hai ( apna haq ) chore den. ( aur poora mohar day den to un ko ikhtiyar hai ) aur agar tum mard log hay apna haq chore do to yeh parhaiz gari ki baat hai. aur aapas mein bhalai karne ko faramosh nah karna. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai
